WorkItem.Description: Since I'm getting close to getting the rotation tables worked out.  Let's start looking at some other key things. Like no Tier sets in the UI.  That should be easy enough to fix.

Comments.Message: The druid pieces were all under "Unknown / Not on Wowhead" for me.    Go into the edit items screen and type in the name of the item and you can see if it is there or not (and also what location data it has attached).
Yeah, current problem isn't that the pieces aren't showing up, but that the Set Bonuses aren't showing up on the Buffs page or via the comparison graph.
